00:33:17.000 --> 00:33:22.000
So we wanted to leave players, you know, with a real sense of satisfaction.

539
00:33:22.360 --> 00:33:23.360
You know, you scratch that.

540
00:33:23.360 --> 00:33:28.360
We wanted players to feel genuinely happy and leave the game with a smile on their face.

541
00:33:28.360 --> 00:33:32.360
So, yeah, we sat down and we kind of made a list of what makes people happy.

542
00:33:32.360 --> 00:33:37.360
And then we kind of made a list of what we could put in a game and then put it into Excel

543
00:33:37.360 --> 00:33:38.360
and pivot table.

