00:33:48.720 --> 00:33:54.720
And so, you know, when all is said and done, a lot of this actually came out of our constraints.

548
00:33:54.720 --> 00:33:55.720
You know, we had a small team.

549
00:33:55.720 --> 00:33:57.720
We had a limited amount of time.

