552
00:34:08.720 --> 00:34:10.720
was really high.

553
00:34:11.080 --> 00:34:19.080
So, the moral of the whole thing for us was just try to fully embrace your constraints

554
00:34:19.080 --> 00:34:20.080
as fuel for creativity.

555
00:34:20.080 --> 00:34:25.080
Honestly, without the constraints that we had, I truly believe Portal would not be as

556
00:34:25.080 --> 00:34:27.080
good a game as it turned out to be.

557
00:34:27.080 --> 00:34:30.080
And in addition to that, you know, have faith in yourself.

558
00:34:30.080 --> 00:34:32.080
Have faith in your writing.

559
00:34:32.080 --> 00:34:37.080
And in the skills of your team, because, you know, they're your best resources.

560
00:34:37.440 --> 00:34:41.440
And, once again, playtest, playtest, playtest.

